snippet.title: Stellar Blade - The Journey (Behind The Scenes) | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/stellar-blade/

Meet the talented creators at SHIFT UP, discover the origins of Stellar Blade™, and learn more about the incredible journey this project took to come to life.

Reclaim Earth for Humankind in Stellar Blade, launching April 26, 2024 only on PS5® console.
Pre-order now for in-game bonuses.

#ps5games #ps5 #StellarBlade
